# IFX Monocle - Inner Source Usage and Metrics Tracker

[![Supported versions](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.9%20%7C%203.10%20%7C%203.11%20%7C%203.12-blue)](https://gitlab.intra.infineon.com/global_projects/PyVerify-Ecosystem/misc/ifx-monocle)
